{"tid":2165981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女學生急救途中被救護車直送殯儀館","createTime":"2020-08-20T07:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T23:45:25.000Z","uid":251052,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3a263390639c04b91d115d5142bc5c5a792b9861","tid":2165981,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2646787905465679/?extid=GIomg84G4FtHNvCY&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2646787905465679%2F%3Fextid%3DGIomg84G4FtHNvCY%26d%3Dn&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRuffDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=967b3726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2646787905465679/?extid=GIomg84G4FtHNvCY&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【女學生急救途中被救護車直送殯儀館】<br />\n<br />\n六月中江蘇鹽城一個中三女學生，在課室突然暈倒，校方隨即送她到衛生院，同時叫救護車。<br />\n<br />\n女生母親說，急救員趕到衛生院時，指該女生已沒有生命跡象，但在衛生院勸喻下，答應送女生到縣人民醫院搶救，但救護車直接開到殯儀館，跟車的老師投訴，而且殯儀館基於沒有醫院死亡證拒收後，再把女生送到醫院搶救，最終女生死亡。<br />\n<br />\n官方回應指是安撫家屬，才把女生抬上救護車，做法合規。<br />\n<br />\n#送院變送殯儀館<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"a3e18b315c94cbdad29d441db26ec67b019e2024","tid":2165981,"uid":78873,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"這官方做得不對　器官還未割下來怎能直送火化了?"},{"pid":"2fa6ef0300d36b14577f283934638bd4011bfa1a","tid":2165981,"uid":39653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3e18b315c94cbdad29d441db26ec67b019e2024","tid":2165981,"uid":78873,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"這官方做得不對　器官還未割下來怎能直送火化了?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:31:55.000Z","msg":"跟隨國家指示 n-1 無死人 沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42806d6f5003fbf898c49c0dcaffc2181c2e3223","tid":2165981,"uid":81312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"